title: Browning Hunting Game by Valusoft [PC][1997]
description:
Browning Hunting Game Special Edition
Released: 1999
Windows XP

Originally released in 1997 as 'The Hunting Game' by Valusoft,
rebranded and released as Browning Hunting Game Special Edition
in 1999.

Hunt over 14 species with a variety of weapons, buy your gear at the sports shop, don't forget to buy a license! Super fun old school game.

-----------------------------------------
You may want to run the setup as administrator to avoid
a bunch of security pop-ups, but it's not required.
-----------------------------------------

Mount the ISO, install and then click PLAY!

Tested on Windows 10.

Release by TNT because I couldn't find it on the internet. Enjoy!
